# Load Libraries
```{r message=FALSE}
library(dlookr)
library(glue)
library(here)
library(tidyverse)
```

# Setup
```{r}
data_name <- "<data-name>"
```

# Read Data
```{r}
wrangle_data <- read_rds(here(glue("data/wrangle/{data_name}.rds")))
```

# Explore Data
```{r}
eda_web_report(wrangle_data)
```
